{"tid":1381887,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"戚繼光鴛鴦陣","createTime":"2019-07-29T10:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T11:26:40.000Z","uid":79589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cbfb29004fe692e3e70abe47ff7365c5311652f9","tid":1381887,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:43:29.000Z","msg":"有冇史撚有研究過點應用？<br />\n<br />\n以小隊形式作戰<br />\n前方設2盾兵抵擋近身打<br />\n後方4至8人，用長棍類武器制敵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/kknews.cc/history/nvj83a5.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhistory%2Fnvj83a5.amp&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2Bn88up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=96789e1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/kknews.cc/history/nvj83a5.amp</a>"},{"pid":"18ba3423440e6d44559a19379ab6b69e7872dc29","tid":1381887,"uid":229019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NX7EMKA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNX7EMKA.jpg&h=990f4b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aEiXypB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaEiXypB.jpg&h=020f3ad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ans9pwg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAns9pwg.png&h=b8d6d814&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f317b6a0288a78714a2d4e81dd6a4f89dc11fc23","tid":1381887,"uid":290542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NahhywS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNahhywS.jpg&h=8d878c92&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n恕我用下一D內地既研究，雖然有說師夷之長技以制夷，不過情況不同，鴛鴦陣係個有引誘性的戰陣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rB75Hrv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrB75Hrv.jpg&h=83e5eb15&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n前面兩個盾兵配標槍，對面有一定距離沖前個陣，會將標槍投擲出去進攻(但尼套依家唔WORK，因為槍既射程比標槍遠，盾牌兵數量又唔夠亦會被海綿彈之類既射穿)<br />\n<br />\n中間狼筅兵用來壓制對面部隊沖前肉搏，因為佢地兵器既特性充滿倒刺同鐵枝可以釣住長槍之類既兵器，我諗對警棍都有一定既壓制力，不過相比起長槍，警棍好發力好多，所以我對尼樣野既功用暫時仲係表示懷疑<br />\n<br />\n後面長矛係殺傷既主力，不過現實考慮充其量都係用竹棍。咁實用性同威脅力就大大不如。<br />\n<br />\n最尾個把钂鈀係過於屈機既殺傷性兵器，可以當發射架當丫叉咁射，可以當狼筅咁卡住支棍，又可以用來衝刺，雖然睇上去非常美好但又有個好現實既問題，就係尼樣野一D都唔易用要好長時間練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果唔想傷到巴打"}]}